{"tid":734804,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」用手機上緊連登既入一入黎！","createTime":"2018-07-09T03:29:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T12:50:01.000Z","uid":19889,"like":217,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"017aa97de343d21449b5fa4c27860f292621f786","tid":734804,"uid":19889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"依家d智能手機愈出愈大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n統計下四至五成人係用手指尾托住個電話<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/112453_e69cc44b139d7cce97475a1e94dda45b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F112453_e69cc44b139d7cce97475a1e94dda45b.png&h=db6e1c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n電話本身唔算好重 但長期咁樣用手指尾都托住部電話就好易有smartphone pinky, 影響到骨骼健康<br />\n<br />\n再加埋你老撚咁重既機殻 病情好快惡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/112105_31e3ee8eee86cb9a639b086bb62623fb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F112105_31e3ee8eee86cb9a639b086bb62623fb.png&h=8e8b8c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/112107_893bde9d4f92e15de55b7771670e32e7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F112107_893bde9d4f92e15de55b7771670e32e7.png&h=b68c4740&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/112108_8468e8bbbf43c5b21b8287d6a82de534.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F112108_8468e8bbbf43c5b21b8287d6a82de534.png&h=62b31ceb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/112109_24c40db8952f294d2054b4bca06a7333.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F112109_24c40db8952f294d2054b4bca06a7333.png&h=5a07e9ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家記得用電話果陣要用正確既姿勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/112204_40a89ab8d524e291899275c3b587da80.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F09%2F112204_40a89ab8d524e291899275c3b587da80.png&h=06815b29&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://alistapart.com/d/432/1.4-thumb-zone.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Falistapart.com%2Fd%2F432%2F1.4-thumb-zone.jpg&h=9ff15986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講完手指都有少少痛<br />\n用得手機成粒鐘既你 快d好比隻眼休息啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28d2395a20f9b7d8a9c2b2fa8a3bc5f2602e45b7","tid":734804,"uid":193555,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:55:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c71bbb291687f0c7129412517d0a7e14871c46da","tid":734804,"uid":68794,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"點解用右手會好過用左手？"},{"pid":"f67c5c3c108184ac25b307544fc9bdc0a3017d8e","tid":734804,"uid":188,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:00:56.000Z","msg":"閱"},{"pid":"a92906774b0febf28383668d1ac9b51e84d58567","tid":734804,"uid":12628,"like":19,"dislike":1,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:36:48.000Z","msg":"依家啲小朋友長期玩電話仔先大獲，傷眼又對頸骨發育唔好，大個一定奶野。"},{"pid":"b307604201ef7420bedf81308a9e901895ea885a","tid":734804,"uid":12628,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"c71bbb291687f0c7129412517d0a7e14871c46da","tid":734804,"uid":68794,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T03:57:27.000Z","msg":"點解用右手會好過用左手？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T04:37:31.000Z","msg":"因為左手要手持陽具打飛機"},{"pid":"e7b5408273bd7872d4c0971acd8e7ecc9bd9766e","tid":734804,"uid":165232,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:18:57.000Z","msg":"禁入嚟個陣真係用馬手指尾托住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望下兩隻尾指發現右手尾指真係有個位彎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bc4cf8d874fbc1ba8f6f6f9a129fe5294ee5d9c","tid":734804,"uid":165232,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>禁入嚟個陣真係用手指尾托住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望下兩隻尾指發現右手尾指真係有個位彎左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"191988aee834b0a87a3a7301ae417a2def94d33c","tid":734804,"uid":133519,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:20:55.000Z","msg":"右手手指尾同左手唔同咗樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01dcf504ea4cce45ba822af0aaa37e3083a1b6ce","tid":734804,"uid":1130,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:22:22.000Z","msg":"仆街左右手隻尾指真係唔同樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2becfe74e042e9df87bd5ce80426f284464f912","tid":734804,"uid":23677,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:22:56.000Z","msg":"連登 &gt; 公海 &gt; 連登"},{"pid":"89065bfa369f81c89af312d1a6fd1725cebed84f","tid":734804,"uid":42758,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:24:54.000Z","msg":"留名跟進"},{"pid":"8585cf612af9c645218a955b1284118e71315eca","tid":734804,"uid":49151,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T05:28:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/09/132808_d7a3925c50bde9e82df7e9ae8e632fcb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: